{
  "stem": "15694.10",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Anyway, I remember we were working three weeks in a tunnel.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] my, our work was probably to dig for, against, you know, for the hierarchy of the, of the, of the regime, you know.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Maybe they were already put berths for maybe atom bombs in it because they were working themselves on, on these things actually that didn't make much progress because the one person who could have helped them to create the Wunderwaffen, the military weapons which Hitler promised and never managed to finish it was Einstein.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But as you know, he had to emigrate.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And he helped the, the Americans.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Can't be-- could not be thought out if, what Hitler would have done if he had the atom bomb.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Anyway, the, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] there, the work was very hard.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Again, I asked the German worker, engineers who was drilling, if he could help him.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "He says, yes, you can.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And for the next couple of weeks or so, I thought I had a very easy job.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I was sitting back-to-back with him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "He had the main brunt of the drill, the kango-type drill, whatever it was, primitive, I'm sure, to, against what, how they drill today.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But my bones were shaking so much that in the beginning, I was really afraid that I would collapse.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, but then I said, how to get it secondhand?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But from time to time, I would, so he gave me a bit of bread, which, of course, I shared with my father.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the others were very envious.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I, at one time, thought, well, you can change with me some because it was-- I felt terrible at the beginning.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I got used to it at the end.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
